      "description": "VM."
    },
    {
      "type": "View",
      "path": "jsonui-doc-web/src/app/tools/test-runner/page.tsx",
      "description": "Page."
    }
  ],
  "notes": [
    "Fourth live entry under the Tools tab.",
    "Essay layout (no Collection). Two CodeBlocks illustrate: (a) a test file shape, (b) the CI invocation pattern."
